System-Managed Reports - References 
bookmark_border
On this page
Weekly references

References reports provide a view of all the active reference files and associated matches.



Weekly references

This weekly report lists all of the references provided by a partner and provides important information about reference files, such as exclusions and a mapping of reference IDs to reference video IDs and assets.

The reportType id for this report is content_owner_active_references_a1.

Contents
Primary Key:
reference_id
reference_video_id
asset_custom_id
asset_id

Additional fields:
status
date_created
reference_type
source_of_fingerprint
active_claims
asset_metadata_type
asset_title
asset_labels
asset_owners
provider
length_sec
excluded_perc
exclusions
